=== Condition ===
Child components are applied to each player target if they are crouching or not according to the settings.

=== Options ===
|= Name |= YAML Key |= Type |= Description |
| Crouching | crouch | [[Boolean|_Option Boolean]] | Whether or not the target should be crouching |

=== Description ===
* Crouching is sneaking (shift click)
* Can be used with the [[Crouch|_Trigger Crouch]] to handle both cases

